$interpreted: Jasmine: Not here either...
Dumb Bear Soldier: Jasmine, what you looking for?
Jasmine: I'm looking for exotic plant that can only be found in the desert. It's called "Desert Black King".
Dumb Bear Soldier: Desert Black King? Can we eat it?
Jasmine: The plant itself not edible. However, rumor has it that the fruit's very delicious. I've always wanted to cook with it.
Dumb Bear Soldier: Very delicious? ~~ I want to taste it as well~~
Jasmine: If we can find it, I'll certainly let you try it.
Dumb Bear Soldier: Then let me help you out too.
Handsome Bear: Ugh, this is getting on my nerves! Just when are they going to become a couple!? My Miss Rose is still waiting for me to bring her good news.
Young Master Bear: When has she ever become "Your" Miss Rose??
Young Master Bear: However, if it's about getting those two together, I've got pretty good idea. Have you ever heard about "Suspension Bridge Effect"?
Handsome Bear: You mean by trapping two people in a dangerous place...
Handsome Bear: ... they'll fall in love with each other?
Young Master Bear: Correct, and I know there's a gorge right down the road...
Dumb Bear Soldier: Can't find Black Desert King...
Jasmine: This plant has jagged leaves. On top of that, it also bites people. You need to be extra careful when approaching it.
Dumb Bear Soldier: Plant that bites people? Think I've seen it somewhere...
Dumb Bear Soldier: Muuuu... Can't remember.
Young Master Bear: HELP! Somebody come help us~~
Jasmine: Did those two get themselves in trouble again?
Dumb Bear Soldier: They are in danger~~
Dumb Bear Soldier: AH!!!
Jasmine: Oh no, it's a gorge!
Jasmine: Are you alright?
Dumb Bear Soldier: Owww... hand hurts...
Jasmine: There there, pain pain go away~~
Dumb Bear Soldier: Wow! No hurt anymore! You're amazing!~
Jasmine: Good to see that you're safe...
Dumb Bear Soldier: Little flower?
Dumb Bear Soldier: Bad flower, BAD FLOWER! Let go of Jasmine now!!

Dumb Bear Soldier: Jasmine, don't die... *Cries*...
Please don't die...
Jasmine: Ugh...
Dumb Bear Soldier: JASMINE!! Thank god you're still alive... *sobs*...
Jasmine: Why are you crying so sadly?

Dumb Bear Soldier: I thought Jasmine died.
Thank god you're still alive... *Sobs*...
Jasmine: Are you that worried about me?

Dumb Bear Soldier: Because I love Jasmine very much.
If Jasmine dies, I will be very, very sad.
Jasmine: So love can be this simple too...
Dumb Bear Soldier: Jasmine?
Jasmine: What I mean is, thank you for risking your life and saving me...
Dumb Bear Soldier: You're welcome~~
Jasmine: Too bad this Desert Black King fruit is completely squished. Looks like we'll have to find another one.
Dumb Bear Soldier: Huh? So this is Desert Black King's fruit?
Dumb Bear Soldier: This is same as little flower's fruit~

Jasmine: Eh? It is!
Didn't know that little flower is seedling of the Desert Black King.
Dumb Bear Soldier: That's great. Then I give all of little flower's fruits to Jasmine~
Jasmine: Thank you, after we go back, I will make delicious meals out of these fruits to thank you~

Dumb Bear Soldier: Then let's go back right away~
Want to taste Jasmine's cooking as soon as possible~
Dumb Bear Soldier: Ah...
Jasmine: What's the matter?
Dumb Bear Soldier: Although I'm very excited about big meal, I can no longer eat lunch boxes prepared by Jasmine after we go back...
Jasmine: If you like them so much, after we go back, I can make it for you every day~
Dumb Bear Soldier: For real!?
Jasmine: Of course it's real.
Dumb Bear Soldier: Every day!?

Jasmine: Yes. if you like it so much, 
I will cook it for you every day.
Dumb Bear Soldier: Yahoo~! Lunch boxes every day~
Jasmine: Let's go~
Dumb Bear Soldier: Yep~ let's go~
